Flask Fundamentals

These topics teach you how to build web applications with Flask.

| No. | Topic                                  | Why it is needed                                                       |
| --- | -------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| 1   | Web Development Introduction           | Understand client-server architecture and web applications.            |
| 2   | Decorators                             | Learn `@app.route()` and URL routing in Flask.                         |
| 3   | Simple Web Application                 | Build your first Flask application.                                    |
| 4   | Simple Web App using HTML File         | Display HTML pages with Flask.                                         |
| 5   | Parameter Passing in the Web App       | Pass data through URLs and forms.                                      |
| 6   | Normal Flask App                       | Learn a complete Flask project structure.                              |
| 7   | Normal Flask App with Input and Output | Handle user input and display results.                                 |
| 8   | Input and Output Backend Process       | Understand how requests and responses flow between browser and server. |

Purpose: Learn Flask from the basics.
=====

Flask + Machine Learning

After learning Flask, you connect it to a Machine Learning model.

| No. | Topic                                    | Why it is needed                                                     |
| --- | ---------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| 9   | Machine Learning Application using Flask | Integrate an ML model with Flask.                                    |
| 10  | Deployment File Importance               | Learn about `requirements.txt`, configuration, and deployment files. |
| 11  | Machine Learning Application – 2         | Build a more complete ML web application.                            |

Purpose: Build AI/ML applications using Flask.

=====

Deployment & Productivity

These topics focus on improving and publishing your application.

| No. | Topic                          | Why it is needed                                              |
| --- | ------------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------- |
| 12  | Improving UI with ChatGPT      | Use AI to improve the application's interface.                |
| 13  | ML Deployment on Render        | Publish the Flask application online.                         |
| 14  | How to use ChatGPT for Project | Use ChatGPT to write, debug, and improve code.                |
| 15  | Assignment ML Project          | Build a complete end-to-end project using everything learned. |

Purpose: Make your project professional and deploy it for others to use.

