Learn Flask fundamentals.
Build web applications.
Connect Machine Learning or AI models.
Improve the user interface.
Deploy the application to the cloud.
Complete a real-world project.

So, while the module is called "Web Development using Flask," it doesn't only teach Flask syntax. It teaches how to use Flask as the foundation for building,
enhancing, and deploying complete AI and Machine Learning web applications.

